\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/4775512f1c1cbd0ff8b321d0c9f9d2fa.poster.avif?t=1681424279\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/4775512f1c1cbd0ff8b321d0c9f9d2fa.webm?t=1681424279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/4775512f1c1cbd0ff8b321d0c9f9d2fa.mp4?t=1681424279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/fc6fa19d5af7246e4341d70b31664882.avif?t=1681424279\" width=616 height=104 /></span><br><br>Set in a small town in Spain, the story of Iria and her family is linked to Galician society in the 1990s, as well as to horror cinema and the influence it had on her.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/eaca7a6e8053a6c05bdcf70c8595a3de.poster.avif?t=1681424279\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/eaca7a6e8053a6c05bdcf70c8595a3de.webm?t=1681424279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1910320/extras/eaca7a6e8053a6c05bdcf70c8595a3de.mp4?t=1681424279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
